  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK898">
<l>kuṉṟaṉṉār kuṉṟa matippiṟ kuṭiyoṭu </l>
<l>niṉṟaṉṉār māyvar nilattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If (the) hill-like (devotees) resolve on destruction, those who seemed to be everlasting will be destroyed root and branch from the earth.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
